  <brief_title>Safety, Tolerability, and Efficacy Study of MB07803 Administered to Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, 28-day, Multicenter, Double-Blind,Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy of MB07803 in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
  <sponsors>
